headline: 1 Thing to Know Before Buying IonQ Stock
summary: Quantum computing is getting some attention from investors -- a nice change of pace from the relentless onslaught of artificial intelligence (AI) developments over the past couple of years.  Alphabet's Google recently announced a significant breakthrough with its Willow quantum chip related to error correction, and pure-play quantum computing stock IonQ (NYSE: IONQ) has seen its stock rocket higher over the past few months.  IonQ builds quantum computers and develops quantum networking technology.
